From f50ac8cc7d836920131054080e88d8a7c640c5ab Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Rolv-Apneseth <rolv.apneseth@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 6 Mar 2026 15:17:48 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] providers/hetzner: Add support for network configuration

This should enable the generation of systemd-networkd unit and netplan
configuration files for Hetzner systems. Note that a network connection
is required to request network metadata (no alternative on Hetzner as
far as I can tell).
